                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18120701-16-defend234 t18120701-16-punish106"></join>
               DEATH
            </rs>, aged 47.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex jury, before Mr. Justice Gibbs.</p>
